      "content": "that's exactly what i'm looking for. it's a super strong point. to wrap up the essay, could you help me write a concluding paragraph? i want it to leave the reader feeling like wealth redistribution isn't just an option, but an urgent moral necessity to fix the damage done by these systems.",
